Jenkins Configuration

Packer-demo Job
https://github.com/afranca/packer-demo.git

Build Execute Shell Script
ARTIFACT=`packer build -machine-readable packer-demo.json |awk -F, '$0 ~/artifact,0,id/ {print $6}'`
AMI_ID=`echo $ARTIFACT | cut -d ':' -f2`
echo 'variable "APP_INSTANCE_AMI" { default = "'${AMI_ID}'" }' > amivar.tf
aws s3 cp amivar.tf s3://terraform-state-jenkins-packer-093005032020/amivar.tf


Terraform Job
https://github.com/afranca/terraform-leap_vpc.git
Build Execute Shell Script
aws s3 cp s3://terraform-state-jenkins-packer-093005032020/amivar.tf amivar.tf
touch leapkey
touch leapkey.pub
terraform init
terraform apply -auto-approve -var APP_INSTANCE_COUNT=1 -target aws_instance.app-instance